SECTION 44, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 0.5. (a) On or before September 1, 2019, and each
September 1 thereafter, each school corporation, charter school, and
state accredited nonpublic school that provides transportation for
students must review the school's school bus routes and school bus
safety policies to improve the safety of students and adults.
