SECTION 224. IC 21-42-7-2, AS AMENDED BY P.L.101-2014,
SECTION 2, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 2. (a) Each state educational institution shall adopt
a policy to award educational credit to an individual who:
