SECTION 225. IC 21-48-1-1, AS ADDED BY P.L.254-2017,
SECTION 7, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 1. (a) Each approved postsecondary educational
institution shall adopt a policy to increase awareness of suicide
prevention resources available to students and staff, including:
