(4) The reasons for the notice, including the applicable sections
of this chapter under which the fine has been assessed.
(5) Any deadlines or other times within which the recipient of the
notice may or must act under this chapter.
(6) A list of each person to whom the notice is being sent.
(7) A list of any enclosures included with the notice.
(8) The signature of the director, the director's designated
representative, or the other employee or agent of the agency
responsible for the notice.
