292
SECTION 289. IC 36-7-32.5-9, AS AMENDED BY P.L.213-2025,
SECTION 310, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS
[EFFECTIVE JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 9. (a) Before the corporation may
designate territory within the jurisdiction of a city, town, or county, or
within the jurisdiction of more than one (1) city, town, or county, as an
innovation development district under this section, the board of the
